更新字典內容 
#!/usr/bin/env python
#coding=utf-8

dict = {'Name': 'Zara', 'Age': 27, 'Class': 'First'}
 
dict['Age'] = 38 
dict['School'] = "KSU" 
 
print "dict['Age']: ", dict['Age']
print "dict['School']: ", dict['School']
->
dict['Age']:  38
dict['School']:  KSU



列表|串列(list)資料型態及其運算 ->排序是0 1 2 3 ...第一個是0
#!/usr/bin/env python
#coding=utf-8
 
list1 = ['physics', 'chemistry', 1997, 2000]
list2 = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 ]
 
print "list1[0]: ", list1[0] ## 0是第一個
print "list2[1:5]: ", list2[1:5] ## list2[1:5]是1到4
->
list1[0]:  physics
list2[1:5]:  [2, 3, 4, 5]
```
字串(string)資料型態及其運算
```
#!/usr/bin/env python
#coding=utf-8

var1 = 'Hello World!'
var2 = "Python Runoob"
 
print "var1[0]: ", var1[0]
print "var2[1:5]: ", var2[1:5]
->
```
var1[0]:  H
var2[1:5]:  ytho
```
